cts of these drugs and in whom toxicity symptoms may be easily overlooked.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/145649/', '', 'Amoxapine, Viloxazine', 'Nortriptyline', 1767369485);
